(3,	7,	'Inspired Shop Builder Clothing ',	'<p>Polyester micro poplin, so it\'s perfect for outdoor sports and adventures. For convenient storage, the zipped hidden pouch pocket pulls out, and the whole jacket can be packed into&nbsp;</p>',	'<ul><li>100% polyester micro poplin</li><li>Wind and rain resistant</li><li>Half-zip pullover with a hood</li><li>Front kangaroo pocket</li><li>Hidden zipped pouch pocket</li><li>Packable in the zipped pouch pocket</li><li>Adjustable bungee drawcord at hood and bottom hem</li><li>Elastic cuffs</li><li>Embroidered “C” logo on the left sleeve</li><li>Available for left chest embroidery</li><li>Blank product sourced from Vietnam</li></ul>',	'CLS-12432',	7000,	'free',	0,	'0',	'',	0,	0,	500,	0,	'amount',	0,	1,	NULL),
(4,	8,	'Start your morning with COmmerceLab',	'<p>This sturdy mug is perfect for your morning coffee, afternoon tea, or whatever hot beverage you enjoy. It\'s glossy white and yields vivid prints that retain their quality when dish-washed and microwaved. Add a graphic of your choice and add this best-seller to your store, so others can enjoy your magical designs too!</p>',	'<ul><li>Ceramic</li><li>11 oz mug dimensions: 3.79″ (9.6 cm) in height, 3.25″ (8.3 cm) in diameter</li><li>15 oz mug dimensions: 4.69″ (11.9 cm) in height, 3.35″ (8.5 cm) in diameter</li><li>Dishwasher and microwave safe</li></ul>',	'',	0,	'none',	0,	'0',	'',	0,	0,	NULL,	0,	'amount',	0,	0,	NULL);